Notes
Works best on Windows, where registry and startup folder scanning are supported.

Classification is keyword-based; programs are flagged if their names match entries in the essential, unnecessary, or harmful lists.

Harmful programs should be removed immediately, while unnecessary programs can be disabled to improve startup speed.

Reports are saved in startup_analysis_report.json for later review.
